// IM 1 INT acceptance. EI then NOP loop; INT pulse mid-loop forces an
// INTA M-cycle (M1+IORQ together) then RST 38h to the IM1 vector at 0x38.
// At 0x38, a HALT so the trace stays well-defined after the ack.
@0000
ED 56              // IM 1
FB                 // EI                       (one-instruction INT-mask)
00 00 00 00        // NOPs (loop)
C3 04 00           // JP 0x0004                (back into the NOP loop)
@0038
76                 // HALT
